data.description: Live in one side and rent out the other. This multifamily home is a 2 unit Side by side home Manville. With hardwood flooring throughout, and nice size eat in kitchen kitchen. Each unit have 2  bedrooms, 1 bath.  Each unit also have access to their own private basement with laundry hookup. The back door leads to to nice size fenced in backyard. There is off street parking with their own driveway. New windows installed in one unit. Walking distance to downtown shopping/Restaurants, and public transportation nearby. Easy access to 287, 22, 202/206 & less than a 10 min. drive to Somerville & Bridgewater Train Stations!  Not in Flood zone!
